short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Do more with less and limit yourself to 10 tabs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you suffer from too many tabs and too little attention? If so, this is the app for you. This simple  open source app to save yourself from tab sprawl, no configuration needed (or supported). Check out the code here: https://github.com/TeaUponTweed/decitab
* We do not count pinned tabs, so pin responsibly!
